              <Para>If we restrict our analysis to times when observed ozone is greater than 100 μg/m3 (ozone episode conditions), which are the times of greatest interest to policymakers due to the possible health impacts [<CitationRef CitationID="CR00795">5</CitationRef>], a different picture emerges, which can be seen from Table <InternalRef RefID="Tab00792">79.2</InternalRef>. <Table Float="Yes" ID="Tab00792">
